  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this study the investigators investigate the effect of a red rice product on plasma lipids
      in a sample of physicians and/or their family members.

      After a baseline measurement of cholesterol, HDL, LDL and TG, participants are randomised to
      receive a commercially available red rice product or placebo. After a period of 8 weeks,
      lipid levels are measured again.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
